data.description: Enjoy the most beautiful sunsets here! 4bd/2ba home on .89 acres. Ask for details on the acre next door to make 2 acres! 3 car oversize garage w/shelving, cabinets & work bench (New LED shop lights). No carpet, over $20,000 in flooring installed 7/2023. Eat-in kitchen combined w/double dining areas, great for entertaining! Recessed dimmable lighting. Updated kitchen counters & sink. All appliances included. 2-way woodburning fireplace. Master bedroom with double door entry & walk-in closet that can be entered from the bedroom or bathroom. Master bathroom has a soaker tub & separate sinks. Lots of storage throughout. 1 bedroom has built-in bunks & loft bed. Covered front & back porch. Concrete walkways. Mature landscaping. Fully fenced w/automatic gate & circular driveway. NO HOA! Plenty of space for your toys, RV, boat, trailers, etc. RV hookups. Chicken coops. Greenhouse w/peppers, tomatoes, chives & birds of paradise. Shed/pump house with fresh paint.
